(102, 'How close are we to a real Iron Man suit?', 'how-close-are-we-to-a-real-iron-man-suit', 'The suit in the movie breaks a lot of rules. Is the suit theoretically possible? Let’s ask ourselves a couple of questions.', '<p>The suit in the movie breaks a lot of rules. Is the suit theoretically possible? Let&rsquo;s ask ourselves a couple of questions.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Question 1: How is a suit able to withstand so much damage and protect the pilot?</strong></p>\r\n<p>In many scenes in the movie, you see Tony Stark get beat up to a pulp. He gets thrown through windows, onto concrete, in Civil War: Captain America a Vibranium shield punches through his armor.</p>\r\n<p>Iron Man&rsquo;s suit is made out of a composite of different materials. In the first movie, the MK-I suit was made up of titanium-nickel alloys. This is protect his breast from further damage. For the boosters on his feet, he would have to use a titanium-nickel alloy that would allow him to boost up to the air.</p>\r\n<p>Tony needs to have cushioning inside of his suit, am I right?</p>\r\n<p>For protection he would need some sort of padding and ballistic mesh. According to Scifi Stack Exchange, there must be some sort of antigravity built into the suit to reduce the damage done to the suit.</p>\r\n<p>Also, the suit has Vibranium. It doesn&rsquo;t exist in our world. To create a suit like this would cost many millions of dollars. That&rsquo;s a luxury only a few governments in the world could afford.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Question 2: How is the energy within the suit generated?</strong></p>\r\n<p>It doesn&rsquo;t exist. How is the arc reactor able to generate power?</p>\r\n<p>In movie canon, the energy is generated through the arc reactor in Tony&rsquo;s chest.</p>\r\n<p>The original arc reactor was used to power Stark Industries. When Yinsen saved Tony&rsquo;s life he placed an arc reactor inside of Tony that not only saved his life but also powered his Iron Man suits.</p>\r\n<p>In Iron Man 2, the same arc reactor was poisoning Tony&rsquo;s body. He created a new arc reactor that was powered by a new element that he synthesized.</p>', '2021-09-27 14:41:59', '2021-09-27 14:43:48', 'Tag3,Tag4', 20, '0eeeee7efbca2fd9584ef35afc07c6b4.jpg'),
(103, 'Why is data labeling for machine learning so important?', 'why-is-data-labeling-for-machine-learning-so-important', 'Supervised training—a strategic combination of human expertise and the latest tools—is required for an AI/ML model to act and make decisions, creating the need for data labeling in machine learning.', '<p>Supervised training&mdash;a strategic combination of human expertise and the latest tools&mdash;is required for an AI/ML model to act and make decisions, creating the need for data labeling in machine learning.</p>\r\n<p>So what is data labeling? It is the process of adding tags and metatags to the input datasets to be fed into the machine learning algorithms. The labels help smart models to calculate attributes easily; input data can be text, audio, video, image, etc.</p>\r\n<p>Going by my experience with various providers, I found Damco Solutions as a client-friendly and reliable company to outsource data labeling services. They offer customized solutions at cost-effective rates. Other lucrative features of this company are as mentioned below:</p>\r\n<p><strong>Competent Professionals</strong></p>\r\n<p>As one of the leading data labeling companies, they have a pool of data professionals and accredited annotators who work as an extended in-house team to provide a collaborative workflow to the clients.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Comprehensive Suite of Offerings</strong></p>\r\n<p>They offer quality image recognition, digital picture annotation, image masking annotation, text annotation, video annotation, 2D and 3D annotation, bounding boxes, cuboids, polygons, semantic segmentation, etc.&mdash;essentially everything under a roof.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Access to Cutting-Edge Technology</strong></p>\r\n<p>Having advanced tools, a time-tested blend of manual workflows, and project-specific execution plans, they strive for excellence in all their data labeling outsourcing endeavors.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Up to 99.99% Accuracy Assured</strong></p>\r\n<p>The professionals can efficiently and accurately label any volumes of data pixel by pixel. By outsourcing your services to them, you can enjoy the benefits of consistent, coherent, and correct data streams within the desired time and budget.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Industry-Compliant Practices</strong></p>\r\n<p>Being a seasoned service provider, the company incorporates data security and all the other important factors while creating an input data set.</p>\r\n<p>Happy Reading!!</p>', '2021-09-27 14:45:46', '2021-09-27 14:47:18', 'Tag3,Tag4', 20, 'ce4594c50d921b0e9c0a1b68e9538b24.png'),
